ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: A very broad and introductory course to geochemistry and highly recommend to those who need the basic knowledge about geochemistry
I think it is good that a fellow student took this class. It teaches you a lot of basic ideas and formulas of geochemistry.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This course provide a general understanding of what and how geochemistry involves and it helps prepare some fundamental knowledge for my research.
Sure, this course taught me a lot of basic principles of geochemistry and now I have a big picture of the geochemistry world.
This course helped me review things I had forgotten and learn things I wasn't able to previously.
